Product description

Set Contents:
Pokmon GO Plus + main unit.
Pokmon GO Plus + strap with dedicated clip.
USB charging cable
Start guide:

Product Size: Diameter approx. 2.5 inches (64.5 mm) (not including buttons) Thickness: approx. 0.7 inches (18.3 mm) (not including buttons).
Weight: Approx. 1.8 oz (50
Function: Sound function, vibration function.
Built-in battery: Li-ion battery
Battery Charging Time: Approx. 3 hours and 30 minutes *Charging via USB Type-C terminal.

The Pokmon Go Plus + cannot be operated by itself.
Requires smartphone (compatible operating systems: Android/iOS) and compatible app "Pokmon GO" or "Pokmon Sleep" (scheduled for summer 2023).
Depending on your smartphone's make, model, operating system version, or usage of individual devices, you may not be able to connect or connect with the corresponding app, or the corresponding apps and this product may not work properly.
For upcoming OS updates or updates on the applicable app side, there may be cases where it will not work properly as the above mentioned periods.
Pokmon GO Plus + is not covered with a warranty card and does not guarantee to repair the case of failure. We do not accept requests for repairs.
Depending on your bedding or bedroom environment, the sleep measurement function may not work properly.

Model Number: PMC-A-WNSAA.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.

5.0 out of 5 stars Consider getting the Plus+ set with the zip-up cover.
Reviewed in Australia on July 30, 2023
Platform For Display: No Amazon ExclusiveEdition: Single ItemVerified Purchase
Fast and free delivery with Amazon Prime to Australia. Works as expected with Pokemon Go and Pokemon Sleep. Plenty of instruction and reviews on-line. After some use I would recommend buyers consider paying the little bit extra for the Plus+ with the exclusive blue zip-up case. This will likely prevent accidental button pushes if you plan to keep this gizmo in a bag or your pocket. (*might also reduce the level of vibration, the buzzing noise and bright flashing light. Both of which can not be turned off and are not necessary if using the automatic catching and spins) From 1 week of use I am wishing I had bought the Plus+ with a case to begin with, and not now be looking for an after-market container. Enjoy.
